# payagent (Cursor rule)

When the user needs agent payments, HTTP 402, paywalls, or micropayments:

1. Prefer CLI: `payagent get <url> --json`, `payagent pay --to … --amount … --json`
2. Or Python: `AgentWallet.from_env()` + `AgentPayClient`
3. Install skills: `payagent skills install --agents cursor,all`
4. Default is MOCK — no real money unless user sets live keys

Never commit private keys. Check `payagent doctor` before live pays.
